tip.text: A secluded hiding place. Found it by coincidence. Step in and you will start your foodie adventure in Mansfield. Who would think of such delicious Thai / Asian food in this area?
Super Tasty Curry Chicken. It is super yummy 😋
Amazingly DELICIOUS & BEAUTIFUL food!! When ur r on the way from Melbourne to Mt Buller or otherwise this is a MUST Pit Stop. Curry chicken, Pork Belly Chinese broccoli, Steam Dumpling a must!!
The Chirasi and Yakitari are good, not bad at all.
